Time Arrival City Train No. Trains to & from Guilin Guilin is a tourist city famous throughout the world, and thousands of tourists visit Guilin every year. But remember, the city has only two railway stations: Guilin Railway Station and Guilin North Railway Station, and limited cities connect with Guilin. In this case, it is better for you to get clear about the Guilin train schedule before visiting the city. Here we provide you with the train schedule for Guilin Railway Station and Guilin North Railway Station. You can search for a train leaving from or going to Guilin. Get clear about the Guilin train schedule before planning a trip to Guilin. China Highlights is pleased to help you with your travel needs.
